"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president invites the leaders of two countries to Washington. This happens as Israel's prime minister says that troops will not leave southern Lebanon. These comments come after a disagreement with US President Donald Trump, who said the Pope is weak on crime.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Invites Leaders\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos invita a los l\u00edderes de dos pa\u00edses a Washington. Esto pasa mientras el primer ministro de Israel dice que las tropas no saldr\u00e1n del sur de L\u00edbano. Estos comentarios vienen despu\u00e9s de un desacuerdo con el presidente de Estados Unidos Donald Trump, quien dijo que el Papa es d\u00e9bil con el crimen.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. Invita a L\u00edderes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Bolsonaro's ally, Alexandre Ramagem, was stopped by immigration agents in Orlando, Florida on Monday. The armed men reportedly escaped capture by using the city's sewer system.\",            \"english_title\": \"Bolsonaro's Ally Stopped\",            \"translated_version\": \"El aliado de Bolsonaro, Alexandre Ramagem, fue detenido por agentes de inmigraci\u00f3n en Orlando, Florida el lunes. Se dice que los hombres armados escaparon usando el sistema de alcantarillado de la ciudad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Aliado de Bolsonaro Detenido\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"At least 16 people were injured in a shooting at a high school on Tuesday. Then, another nine people were killed in a different school shooting on Wednesday.\",            \"english_title\": \"School Shootings\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos 16 personas resultaron heridas en un tiroteo en una escuela secundaria el martes. Luego, otras nueve personas murieron en otro tiroteo escolar el mi\u00e9rcoles.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tiroteos en Escuelas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Former Arsenal goalkeeper Alex Manninger died at the age of 48 after his car was hit by a train.\",            \"english_title\": \"Alex Manninger Dies\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ex portero del Arsenal, Alex Manninger, muri\u00f3 a los 48 a\u00f1os despu\u00e9s de que su coche fue golpeado por un tren.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muere Alex Manninger\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A Ukrainian drone attack killed two people in Russia, according to Moscow. This happened after an Orthodox Easter truce.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukrainian Drone Attack\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ataque de dron ucraniano mat\u00f3 a dos personas en Rusia, seg\u00fan Mosc\u00fa. Esto pas\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de una tregua de Pascua Ortodoxa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque de Dron Ucraniano\"        }    ]}"